metadata.name: Unravel People's MOONBIRDS
metadata.description: Abbreviation for unravel people's MOONBIRDS, which represents an inactive state of pMOONBIRDS. User can participate in a new MOONBIRDS acquirement subscription and will receive unravel people's MOONBIRDS as credit. upMOONBIRDS can be claimed into pMOONBIRDS when the subscription successfully acquires a new MOONBIRDS.
